            <title>[HBASE-12580] Zookeeper instantiated even though we might not need it in the shell</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-12580</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I wrote an alternative registry and connection manager which does not use zookeeper. However the shell still wants to connect to zookeeper NO MATTER WHAT. I can see it for supporting zk_dump but, for some reason even though the shell commands succeed, I get errors scrolling about why it can&apos;t attach to zookeeper&lt;/p&gt;</description>
